bug.short_desc: Back button in API viewer doesn't work any more

long_desc.thetext: When another class is shown, the old class is added to the history. But going back to the last class doesn't work any more.
Seems to be a bug in qx.client.History. I don't understand the reason for this problem however.

The history class has been reimplemented using the approach from yahoo: http://yuiblog.com/blog/2007/02/21/browser-history-manager/
It is API compatible with the old implementation and supports all browsers supported by qooxdoo.
Safari 20. support may be added later.
